MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the KY14 area of Cupar. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 10:37am. Our engineers are on site and the team will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 3pm. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was recorded at 1:03 PM on Wednesday, 30 December 2020.
